
ROLES AND WHICH ACTIONS THEY ENABLE

| *role* | *controller*      | *actions*    |
|--------+-------------------+--------------|
| admin  | users/reports     | %            |
|        | users/users       | %            |
|        | i18n/locales      | %            |
|        | i18n/translations | %            |
|--------+-------------------+--------------|
| editor | statements        | edit, update |
|        |                   |              |
